<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 Grid System ONLY -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap-grid.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    
    <style>
        .subscription-header {
            padding: 20vh 0 10vh;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .intro-text {
            font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-xl);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .benefits-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
        }
        
        .benefit-card {
            background-color: var(--color-surface);
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform var(--transition-base), background-color var(--transition-base);
        }
        
        .benefit-card:hover {
            background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .benefit-title {
            font-family: var(--font-serif);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
        }

        .benefit-desc {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .contact-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, var(--color-bg-alt) 100%);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: var(--spacing-xl);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contact-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .contact-desc {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="theme-dark">
    <!-- Custom Cursor -->
    <div class="cursor-dot"></div>
    <div class="cursor-outline"></div>

    <header class="navbar scrolled">
        <div class="navbar-container">
            <a href="/" class="brand-logo">KURD CUT</a>
            <div class="nav-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Return Home</a>
            </div>
            <button class="mobile-menu-toggle">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="subscription-header fade-up">
            <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);">Elevate Your Business.</h1>
            <h2 class="hero-title secondary"><span class="serif-italic" style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);">Join the Elite.</span></h2>
        </div>

        <p class="intro-text text-center fade-up delay-1">
            Kurd Cut is an exclusive network. We do not offer open registration for businesses. Instead, we manually vet and onboard every barber, salon, and nail business to ensure our customers experience only the highest standard of service.
        </p>

        <div class="benefits-grid fade-up delay-2">
            <div class="benefit-card">
                <h3 class="benefit-title">Premium Discovery</h3>
                <p class="benefit-desc">Position your brand alongside the top grooming and beauty professionals in the region. Gain visibility to a vast network of customers actively seeking high-end services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card">
                <h3 class="benefit-title">Seamless Management</h3>
                <p class="benefit-desc">Receive instant booking requests. Accept or reject with a single tap. Our system automatically handles customer notifications so you can focus on your craft.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card">
                <h3 class="benefit-title">Advanced Analytics</h3>
                <p class="benefit-desc">Unlock a powerful dashboard designed to track your daily revenue, analyze business performance insights, and understand your customer demographics.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-box fade-up delay-1" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);">
            <h2 class="contact-title">Request a Partnership</h2>
            <p class="contact-desc">
                If you believe your business meets the Kurd Cut standard, please reach out to our administration team. We will review your application and guide you through our tailored subscription tiers to set up your exclusive dashboard.
            </p>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-sm); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <a href="mailto:partnerships@kurdcut.com" class="btn-primary large">Email Administration</a>
                <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="btn-secondary large">Call Support</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container footer-grid">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <h2>KURD CUT</h2>
                <p>The premium booking standard.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <div class="link-group">
                    <h4>Platform</h4>
                    <a href="/#discover">Discover</a>
                    <a href="/business-subscription">For Business</a>
                </div>
                <div class="link-group">
                    <h4>Company</h4>
                    <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
                    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Kurd Cut. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
